<!-- Our Story Section -->
<section style="background: #fff; padding: 40px 0;">
    <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <!-- Text Column -->
        <div style="flex: 1 1 350px; min-width: 320px;">
            <h2 style="color: #2563eb; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 18px;">Our Story</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1.08rem; color: #222; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                United Welfare Society (UWS) was born from a simple yet powerful belief: every person deserves access to basic necessities and opportunities for growth. Founded in 2021 in Chittagong, Bangladesh, our organization emerged from the collective efforts of passionate individuals who witnessed the struggles of neglected and underprivileged communities.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 1.08rem; color: #222; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                What started as a small initiative to help local families has grown into a comprehensive organization serving thousands across Bangladesh, including Rohingya refugees in Cox's Bazar. Our journey has been marked by countless stories of transformation, hope, and resilience.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 1.08rem; color: #222;">
                Today, UWS stands as a beacon of hope for those who need it most, providing essential services in education, healthcare, clean water, food security, and emergency response. Our work is guided by the principle that "Charity is Investment, helps you to earn Smiles."
            </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Images Column -->
        <div style="flex: 1 1 400px; min-width: 320px; display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center;">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506744038136-46273834b3fb?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Story 1" style="width: 32%; min-width: 100px; max-width: 140px; border-radius: 10px; object-fit: cover; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);" />
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464983953574-0892a716854b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Story 2" style="width: 32%; min-width: 100px; max-width: 140px; border-radius: 10px; object-fit: cover; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);" />
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500534314209-a25ddb2bd429?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Story 3" style="width: 32%; min-width: 100px; max-width: 140px; border-radius: 10px; object-fit: cover; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);" />
